5978  p->descriptor_index = jdksavdecc_descriptor_entity_get_descriptor_index( base, pos );
5979  p->entity_id = jdksavdecc_descriptor_entity_get_entity_id( base, pos );
5980  p->entity_model_id = jdksavdecc_descriptor_entity_get_entity_model_id( base, pos );
5981  p->entity_capabilities = jdksavdecc_descriptor_entity_get_entity_capabilities( base, pos );
5982  p->talker_stream_sources = jdksavdecc_descriptor_entity_get_talker_stream_sources( base, pos );
5983  p->talker_capabilities = jdksavdecc_descriptor_entity_get_talker_capabilities( base, pos );
5984  p->listener_stream_sinks = jdksavdecc_descriptor_entity_get_listener_stream_sinks( base, pos );
5985  p->listener_capabilities = jdksavdecc_descriptor_entity_get_listener_capabilities( base, pos );
5986  p->controller_capabilities = jdksavdecc_descriptor_entity_get_controller_capabilities( base, pos );
5987  p->available_index = jdksavdecc_descriptor_entity_get_available_index( base, pos );

5989  p->entity_name = jdksavdecc_descriptor_entity_get_entity_name( base, pos );

6260 
6262 struct jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration
6263 {
6264  uint16_t descriptor_type;
6265  uint16_t descriptor_index;
6266  struct jdksavdecc_string object_name;
6267  uint16_t localized_description;
6268  uint16_t descriptor_counts_count;
6269  uint16_t descriptor_counts_offset;
6270 };
6271 
6287 static inline ssize_t jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration_read( struct jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration *p,
6288  void const *base,
6289  ssize_t pos,
6290  size_t len )
6291 {
6292  ssize_t r = jdksavdecc_validate_range( pos, len, JDKSAVDECC_DESCRIPTOR_CONFIGURATION_LEN );
6293  if ( r >= 0 )
6294  {
6295  p->descriptor_type = jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration_get_descriptor_type( base, pos );
6296  p->descriptor_index = jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration_get_descriptor_index( base, pos );
6297  p->object_name = jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration_get_object_name( base, pos );
6298  p->localized_description = jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration_get_localized_description( base, pos );
6299  p->descriptor_counts_count = jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration_get_descriptor_counts_count( base, pos );
6300  p->descriptor_counts_offset = jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration_get_descriptor_counts_offset( base, pos );
6301  }
6302  return r;
6303 }
6304 
6319 static inline ssize_t jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration_write( struct jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration const *p,
6320  void *base,
6321  size_t pos,
6322  size_t len )
6323 {
6324  ssize_t r = jdksavdecc_validate_range( pos, len, JDKSAVDECC_DESCRIPTOR_CONFIGURATION_LEN );
6325  if ( r >= 0 )
6326  {
6327  jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration_set_descriptor_type( p->descriptor_type, base, pos );
6328  jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration_set_descriptor_index( p->descriptor_index, base, pos );
6329  jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration_set_object_name( p->object_name, base, pos );
6330  jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration_set_localized_description( p->localized_description, base, pos );
6331  jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration_set_descriptor_counts_count( p->descriptor_counts_count, base, pos );
6332  jdksavdecc_descriptor_configuration_set_descriptor_counts_offset( p->descriptor_counts_offset, base, pos );
6333  }
6334  return r;
6335 }

9155  uint16_t clock_domain_index;
9156  uint16_t number_of_stream_input_ports;
9157  uint16_t base_stream_input_port;
9158  uint16_t number_of_stream_output_ports;
9159  uint16_t base_stream_output_port;
9160  uint16_t number_of_external_input_ports;
9161  uint16_t base_external_input_port;
9162  uint16_t number_of_external_output_ports;
9163  uint16_t base_external_output_port;
9164  uint16_t number_of_internal_input_ports;
9165  uint16_t base_internal_input_port;
9166  uint16_t number_of_internal_output_ports;
9167  uint16_t base_internal_output_port;
9168  uint16_t number_of_controls;
9169  uint16_t base_control;
9170  uint16_t number_of_signal_selectors;
9171  uint16_t base_signal_selector;
9172  uint16_t number_of_mixers;
9173  uint16_t base_mixer;
9174  uint16_t number_of_matrices;
9175  uint16_t base_matrix;
9176  uint16_t number_of_splitters;
9177  uint16_t base_splitter;
9178  uint16_t number_of_combiners;
9179  uint16_t base_combiner;
9180  uint16_t number_of_demultiplexers;
9181  uint16_t base_demultiplexer;
9182  uint16_t number_of_multiplexers;
9183  uint16_t base_multiplexer;
9184  uint16_t number_of_transcoders;

9204 static inline ssize_t
9205  jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_read( struct jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit *p, void const *base, ssize_t pos, size_t len )
9206 {
9207  ssize_t r = jdksavdecc_validate_range( pos, len, JDKSAVDECC_DESCRIPTOR_VIDEO_UNIT_LEN );
9208  if ( r >= 0 )
9209  {
9210  p->descriptor_type = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_descriptor_type( base, pos );
9211  p->descriptor_index = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_descriptor_index( base, pos );
9212  p->object_name = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_object_name( base, pos );
9213  p->localized_description = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_localized_description( base, pos );
9214  p->clock_domain_index = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_clock_domain_index( base, pos );
9215  p->number_of_stream_input_ports = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_number_of_stream_input_ports( base, pos );
9216  p->base_stream_input_port = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_base_stream_input_port( base, pos );
9217  p->number_of_stream_output_ports = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_number_of_stream_output_ports( base, pos );
9218  p->base_stream_output_port = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_base_stream_output_port( base, pos );
9219  p->number_of_external_input_ports = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_number_of_external_input_ports( base, pos );
9220  p->base_external_input_port = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_base_external_input_port( base, pos );
9221  p->number_of_external_output_ports = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_number_of_external_output_ports( base, pos );
9222  p->base_external_output_port = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_base_external_output_port( base, pos );
9223  p->number_of_internal_input_ports = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_number_of_internal_input_ports( base, pos );
9224  p->base_internal_input_port = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_base_internal_input_port( base, pos );
9225  p->number_of_internal_output_ports = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_number_of_internal_output_ports( base, pos );
9226  p->base_internal_output_port = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_base_internal_output_port( base, pos );
9227  p->number_of_controls = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_number_of_controls( base, pos );
9228  p->base_control = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_base_control( base, pos );
9229  p->number_of_signal_selectors = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_number_of_signal_selectors( base, pos );
9230  p->base_signal_selector = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_base_signal_selector( base, pos );
9231  p->number_of_mixers = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_number_of_mixers( base, pos );
9232  p->base_mixer = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_base_mixer( base, pos );
9233  p->number_of_matrices = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_number_of_matrices( base, pos );
9234  p->base_matrix = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_base_matrix( base, pos );
9235  p->number_of_splitters = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_number_of_splitters( base, pos );
9236  p->base_splitter = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_base_splitter( base, pos );
9237  p->number_of_combiners = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_number_of_combiners( base, pos );
9238  p->base_combiner = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_base_combiner( base, pos );
9239  p->number_of_demultiplexers = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_number_of_demultiplexers( base, pos );
9240  p->base_demultiplexer = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_base_demultiplexer( base, pos );
9241  p->number_of_multiplexers = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_number_of_multiplexers( base, pos );
9242  p->base_multiplexer = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_base_multiplexer( base, pos );
9243  p->number_of_transcoders = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_unit_get_number_of_transcoders( base, pos );

12505  p->descriptor_index = jdksavdecc_descriptor_avb_interface_get_descriptor_index( base, pos );

12509  p->interface_flags = jdksavdecc_descriptor_avb_interface_get_interface_flags( base, pos );
12510  p->clock_identity = jdksavdecc_descriptor_avb_interface_get_clock_identity( base, pos );
12511  p->priority1 = jdksavdecc_descriptor_avb_interface_get_priority1( base, pos );
12512  p->clock_class = jdksavdecc_descriptor_avb_interface_get_clock_class( base, pos );
12513  p->offset_scaled_log_variance = jdksavdecc_descriptor_avb_interface_get_offset_scaled_log_variance( base, pos );
12514  p->clock_accuracy = jdksavdecc_descriptor_avb_interface_get_clock_accuracy( base, pos );
12515  p->priority2 = jdksavdecc_descriptor_avb_interface_get_priority2( base, pos );

16887  size_t len )

16893  p->descriptor_index = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_cluster_get_descriptor_index( base, pos );

16899  p->path_latency = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_cluster_get_path_latency( base, pos );
16900  p->block_latency = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_cluster_get_block_latency( base, pos );
16901  p->format = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_cluster_get_format( base, pos );
16902  p->current_format_specific = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_cluster_get_current_format_specific( base, pos );
16903  p->supported_format_specifics_offset
16904  = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_cluster_get_supported_format_specifics_offset( base, pos );
16905  p->supported_format_specifics_count
16906  = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_cluster_get_supported_format_specifics_count( base, pos );
16907  p->current_sampling_rate = jdksavdecc_descriptor_video_cluster_get_current_sampling_rate( base, pos );
16908  p->supported_sampling_rates_offset

18806 static inline ssize_t
18807  jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_read( struct jdksavdecc_descriptor_control *p, void const *base, ssize_t pos, size_t len )
18808 {
18809  ssize_t r = jdksavdecc_validate_range( pos, len, JDKSAVDECC_DESCRIPTOR_CONTROL_LEN );
18810  if ( r >= 0 )
18811  {
18812  p->descriptor_type = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_get_descriptor_type( base, pos );
18813  p->descriptor_index = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_get_descriptor_index( base, pos );
18814  p->object_name = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_get_object_name( base, pos );
18815  p->localized_description = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_get_localized_description( base, pos );
18816  p->block_latency = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_get_block_latency( base, pos );
18817  p->control_latency = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_get_control_latency( base, pos );
18818  p->control_domain = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_get_control_domain( base, pos );
18819  p->control_value_type = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_get_control_value_type( base, pos );
18820  p->control_type = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_get_control_type( base, pos );
18821  p->reset_time = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_get_reset_time( base, pos );
18822  p->values_offset = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_get_values_offset( base, pos );
18823  p->number_of_values = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_get_number_of_values( base, pos );
18824  p->signal_type = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_get_signal_type( base, pos );
18825  p->signal_index = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_get_signal_index( base, pos );
18826  p->signal_output = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_get_signal_output( base, pos );
18827  }
18828  return r;
18829 }

24026 static inline ssize_t jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_block_read( struct jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_block *p,
24027  void const *base,
24028  ssize_t pos,
24029  size_t len )
24030 {
24031  ssize_t r = jdksavdecc_validate_range( pos, len, JDKSAVDECC_DESCRIPTOR_CONTROL_BLOCK_LEN );
24032  if ( r >= 0 )
24033  {
24034  p->descriptor_type = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_block_get_descriptor_type( base, pos );
24035  p->descriptor_index = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_block_get_descriptor_index( base, pos );
24036  p->object_name = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_block_get_object_name( base, pos );
24037  p->localized_description = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_block_get_localized_description( base, pos );
24038  p->number_of_controls = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_block_get_number_of_controls( base, pos );
24039  p->base_control = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_block_get_base_control( base, pos );
24040  p->final_control_index = jdksavdecc_descriptor_control_block_get_final_control_index( base, pos );
24041  }
24042  return r;
24043 }
